document_data.Usage:
* Smelling salts were useful for waking up those who had been knocked unconscious or put to sleep, magically or otherwise.{{Cite dragon/69/Ready for anything!|64}} It could even break some mental [[enchantment]]s.{{Cite dragon/234/Nocturnal Crusade|10}}
* ''[[Brightmantle]]'' used smelling salts or similar ammonia-based substances as a [[material component]].
* ''[[Modify memory]]'' could use smelling salts as a [[metamagic]] component.
